---
// Solutions.astro - Three platform cards section
---

<section class="section" id="solutions">
  <div class="section-tag" data-i18n="sol_tag">Pilih Platform</div>
  <h2><span data-i18n="sol_h2_line1">Tiga Cara Deploy</span><br /><em data-i18n="sol_h2_em">Satu Tujuan</em></h2>
  <p class="section-lead" data-i18n="sol_lead">
    Kami menyediakan solusi WA Order yang fleksibel ‚Äî sesuaikan dengan
    infrastruktur dan kebutuhan bisnis Anda.
  </p>

  <div class="cards reveal">
    <!-- Card 1: Self Hosted -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-badge badge-flexible" data-i18n="sol1_badge">Fleksibel</div>
      <div class="card-icon">üñ•Ô∏è</div>
      <div class="card-tag">Self Hosted</div>
      <h3 data-i18n="sol1_title">Node.js / Docker App</h3>
      <p data-i18n="sol1_desc">Deploy di server Anda sendiri. Full control atas data, kustomisasi, dan integrasi apapun. Cocok untuk developer dan bisnis yang butuh privasi penuh.</p>
      <ul class="card-features">
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f1">WhatsApp via Baileys / WWebJS</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f2">Backend Node.js + Express</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f3">Database MySQL / MongoDB</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f4">REST API untuk integrasi</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f5">Docker Compose siap pakai</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f6">Admin Dashboard (React)</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol1_f7">Multi-session WA support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <!-- Card 2: WordPress Plugin -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-badge badge-popular" data-i18n="sol2_badge">Populer</div>
      <div class="card-icon">üîå</div>
      <div class="card-tag">WordPress Theme</div>
      <h3 data-i18n="sol2_title">Tema Siap Pakai</h3>
      <p data-i18n="sol2_desc">Tema WordPress siap pakai tanpa perlu instalasi tambahan. Pasang, aktifkan, dan mulai terima order WA dari toko online Anda dalam hitungan menit.</p>
      <ul class="card-features">
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f1">Tema .zip siap install</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f2">Tidak butuh plugin tambahan</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f3">Notif order real-time ke WA</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f4">Tombol "Pesan via WA" di produk</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f5">Template pesan kustom</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f6">Support multi-admin WA</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol2_f7">Compatible WordPress 6.x</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <!-- Card 3: Odoo Module -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-badge badge-enterprise" data-i18n="sol3_badge">Enterprise</div>
      <div class="card-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
      <div class="card-tag">Odoo Module</div>
      <h3 data-i18n="sol3_title">Odoo 16/17 Integration</h3>
      <p data-i18n="sol3_desc">Modul Odoo yang mengintegrasikan WhatsApp langsung ke alur penjualan, faktur, dan inventori. Ideal untuk bisnis yang sudah menggunakan Odoo ERP.</p>
      <ul class="card-features">
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f1">Modul Odoo 16 & 17</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f2">Sinkron Sales Order & Invoice</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f3">Kirim konfirmasi order via WA</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f4">Reminder pembayaran otomatis</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f5">Notif status pengiriman</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f6">Multi-company support</li>
        <li data-i18n="sol3_f7">Log percakapan di Chatter</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-tag::before {
    content: "";
    width: 20px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--green);
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.06);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .card:hover {
    background: #0f1a16;
  }

  .card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--green);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .card:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-tag {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-family: "Syne", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .card-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .card-features li {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card-features li::before {
    content: "‚úì";
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.2rem;
    right: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .badge-popular {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .badge-flexible {
    background: rgba(170, 238, 68, 0.15);
    color: var(--lime);
    border: 1px solid rgba(170, 238, 68, 0.3);
  }

  .badge-enterprise {
    background: rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.08);
    color: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
